{"tid":2363702,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人買咗《逆統戰》","createTime":"2021-01-12T11:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T03:55:52.000Z","uid":363436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbe5a518d44399bd44fb876232389e87f755479","tid":2363702,"uid":363436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"本遊戲內容物基於特殊考量選在海外生產，物件生產已趨完成，然受冬季疫情回溫影響，發生國際物流緊繃、航運遲滯、海運貨櫃緊缺等情況，導致本遊戲在物料運送與組裝等環節發生預期外的長時間耽擱。開發組目前評估臺澎金馬第一批出貨期程可能因此延宕，特此通知贊助人。<br />\n<br />\n目前估計臺澎金馬第一批出貨期程至多可能延遲3週至4週，但開發組仍會持續催促作業，以求及早出貨。（海外地區出貨期程依地區而異，亦將隨之調整。）<br />\n<br />\n以上情形造成國內贊助人的不便，開發組謹此致上深摯的歉意，希望能獲各位贊助人理解與原諒！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又唔出貨吊胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Freversedfront&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=a180e1b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront</a>"},{"pid":"1fda00544fe85ab2c97bc0c1f963fb90342f9d25","tid":2363702,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"果陣冇訂有冇途徑訂返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee26f96ae996ec4f288b56d0c08182ac002af6a5","tid":2363702,"uid":363436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fda00544fe85ab2c97bc0c1f963fb90342f9d25","tid":2363702,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"果陣冇訂有冇途徑訂返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"唔係官方唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji